    "updated_at": "2017-01-03T23:24:39Z",
    "body": "This is a bug of Chromium, and is fixed in chrome 55, see https://codereview.chromium.org/2350743003/. The latest Electron is based chrome 53, and we are fighting on Chrome 54 upgrade.\r\n\r\nYou could fix that by check-pick the chromium upstream fix and built your own libchromiumcontent and electron, otherwise, you need to wait until electron gets upgrade to chrome 55."
